JO  - Management Science
SP  - 341
EP  - 343
VL  - 9
IS  - 2
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - Certain Properties of Connectivity Matrices are noted to be similarly applicable to Three Management Science Models which have hitherto been investigated as independent structures: (1) PERT Network Analysis; (2) Parts Explosion Techniques; and (3) Business System Data Flow Analysis. These properties suggest some computational techniques which should be helpful in the analysis of systems described by the three models.
